commit.message:
Quiet the python 3.8 deprecation warning (#7)

Abstract classes are now meant to be called from collections.abc instead
of collections.  This will throw an error beginning in python 3.8.
Remove py26 and py34, add py37 and py38

Remove TypeError processing

Don't see reasons to do that
